How old is Drew Gooden?

Drew Gooden is 44 years old.

Drew Gooden was born in Oakland, California.

Drew Gooden was born on September 24, 1981.

How tall is Drew Gooden?

Drew Gooden is 6-10 (208 cm) tall.

How much did Drew Gooden weigh when playing?

Drew Gooden weighed 250 lbs (113 kg) when playing.

Is Drew Gooden in the Hall of Fame?

Drew Gooden is not in the Hall of Fame.

When was Drew Gooden drafted?

Power Forward, Center, and Small Forward.

When did Drew Gooden retire?

Drew Gooden last played in 2016.

What is Drew Gooden's net worth?

Drew Gooden made at least $67,930,972 playing professional basketball.

What did Drew Gooden average?

Drew Gooden won 0 championships.

Drew Gooden attended El Cerrito in El Cerrito, California and Kansas.
